## Setup
```sh
  npm install transformation-matrix
```
## Usage example (ES6)
```sh
import {scale, rotate, translate, transform} from 'transformation-matrix';

let matrix = transform(
  translate(40,40),
  rotate(Math.PI/2),
  scale(2, 4)
);
let point = applyToPoint(matrix, {42, 42});
```
